n      \"a10\": \"Airlines usually handle delays directly. However, our support team can assist you in finding alternatives if needed.\",\n      \"q11\": \"How can I change my profile information?\",\n      \"a11\": \"Go to Profile > Edit Profile to update your name, email, or phone number.\",\n      \"q12\": \"Is my data secure?\",\n      \"a12\": \"Yes, we use industry-standard encryption to protect your personal and payment data.\",\n      \"q13\": \"Do I need a visa for my trip?\",\n      \"a13\": \"Visa requirements depend on your destination and nationality. We recommend checking with the embassy or using our visa service assistance.\",\n      \"q14\": \"Can I pay in installments?\",\n      \"a14\": \"Currently, we offer full payment options. Check back later for installment plans.\",\n      \"q15\": \"Where can I find my booking voucher?\",\n      \"a15\": \"Your voucher is emailed to you and also available in the 'My Bookings' section of the app.\",\n      \"q16\": \"How do I reset my password?\",\n      \"a16\": \"On the login screen, tap 'Forgot Password' and follow the instructions sent to your email.\",\n      \"q17\": \"Are taxes included in the price?\",\n      \"a17\": \"Yes, all prices displayed include applicable taxes unless stated otherwise.\",\n      \"q18\": \"Can I add special requests?\",\n      \"a18\": \"Yes, you can add notes (e.g., dietary preferences, wheelchair access) during the booking process.\",\n      \"q19\": \"What is the baggage allowance?\",\n      \"a19\": \"Baggage policies vary by airline and ticket class. Check your specific flight details for this information.\",\n      \"q20\": \"How do I leave a review?\",\n      \"a20\": \"After your trip is completed, you will receive a notification to rate your experience and leave feedback.\",\n      \"q21\": \"Can I book a car rental?\",\n      \"a21\": \"Yes, we offer car rental services in many destinations. Look for the 'Car Rental' section on the home screen.\",\n      \"q22\": \"Do you offer travel insurance?\",\n      \"a22\": \"Yes, we highly recommend adding travel insurance to your booking for peace of mind. You can select it during checkout.\",\n      \"q23\": \"How can I request an invoice?\",\n      \"a23\": \"Invoices are automatically generated and available in your booking details or sent to your email.\",\n      \"q24\": \"What is the maximum number of people per booking?\",\n      \"a24\": \"This depends on the service provider. Generally, for hotels, it's 3-4 per room; for groups, please contact our support.\",\n      \"q25\": \"Are there any hidden fees?\",\n      \"a25\": \"No, we believe in transparency. All mandatory fees are shown before you confirm your booking.\",\n      \"q26\": \"Can I earn points on every booking?\",\n      \"a26\": \"Yes, all verified bookings earn you membership points based on your current tier.\",\n      \"q27\": \"What is the loyalty program?\",\n      \"a27\": \"Our loyalty program rewards frequent travelers with points, exclusive deals, and tier-based benefits like room upgrades.\",\n      \"q28\": \"Can I change my flight date?\",\n      \"a28\": \"Date changes are subject to airline availability and fees. Contact our support team to check your options.\",\n      \"q29\": \"How do I know if my payment was successful?\",\n      \"a29\": \"You will see a confirmation screen and receive an instant email notification once the payment is processed.\",\n      \"q30\": \"Do you have a mobile app for Android and iOS?\",\n      \"a30\": \"Yes, the Altayar app is available on both the Google Play Store and Apple App Store.\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"wallet\": {\n    \"title\": \"My Wallet\",\n    \"balance\": \"Current Balance\",\n    \"transactions\": \"Transactions\",\n    \"noTransactions\": \"No transactions yet\",\n    \"empty\": \"No transactions found\",\n    \"currency\": \"USD\",\n    \"transaction\": \"Transaction\"\n  },\n  \"points\": {\n    \"title\": \"My Points\",\n    \"available\": \"Availabl